                <h1>My memories from four years of Duke basketball</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/e1ed637a-5941-4bfa-90ea-7baa7052a1d8.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Mike&#x20;Krzyzewski&#x20;and&#x20;mentor&#x20;Bob&#x20;Knight&#x20;embrace&#x20;after&#x20;Krzyzewski&#x20;won&#x20;his&#x20;record-setting&#x20;903rd&#x20;game." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Mike Krzyzewski and mentor Bob Knight embrace after Krzyzewski won his record-setting 903rd game.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
